  <name>Flatpak Portable Builder</name>
  <summary>Create Flatpak packages from Windows PortableApps</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      Flatpak Portable Builder is a tool that allows you to convert Windows PortableApps
      into Flatpak packages using Wine. This makes it easy to distribute and run Windows
      portable applications on Linux systems with proper desktop integration.
    </p>
    <p>
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Import Windows PortableApps</li>
      <li>Configure Wine environment</li>
      <li>Generate Flatpak manifests</li>
      <li>Build and install Flatpak packages</li>
      <li>Support for DXVK for DirectX games</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
